#

Lobster Risotto

40 min
$30
650 kcal
Difficulty: 40%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

ShellfishDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeSeafoodHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main CourseDinner

Tags:

CreamyLuxuryComfort Food

Description

A creamy and luxurious risotto infused with succulent lobster meat, perfect for a special occasion!

Ingredients

  • arborio rice: 1 cup
  • lobster meat: 1 cup, cooked and chopped
  • chicken or seafood broth: 4 cups
  • shallots: 1, finely chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • white wine: 1/2 cup
  • parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • fresh parsley: for garnish
